a financial services behemoth with thousands of employees and tens of billi=
ons of dollars under management, and you=E2=80=99re now at retirement age, =
the tension is:
=09On the one hand, it is very important to transition your firm into an in=
stitution that can work without you: You owe it to your employees and to yo=
